              orcid: "ORCID: 0009-0008-8269-2034",
              aboutData:
                "Ms. Khushnuma Ashraf is a dedicated academician currently serving as an Assistant Professor \, with over twelve years of teaching experience. She has actively participated in several advanced Faculty Development Programs (FDPs) and technical training sessions conducted by premier institutions such as IITs, Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam Technical University (AKTU), and the ATAL Academy. Her areas of interest include Networking, Data Structures, Computer Architecture & Organization, and Web Technology. She adopts an innovative and student-centric approach to teaching, emphasizing the use of modern ideas and techniques to enhance conceptual understanding and practical skills. Committed to continuous professional growth, Ms. Ashraf consistently strives to upgrade her knowledge and teaching methodologies in line with emerging trends in the field of computer science.",
