              aboutData: ` Er. Dinesh is an Assistant Professor in the Department of Mechanical Engineering at SRMCEM. He has a teaching experience of 18 years. His area of specialization is Industrial System Engineering. He has attended several international conferences held at SRMCEM and attended a workshop “MISSION 10X” organized by Wipro to improve teaching quality. He has completed the Human values certificate course up to level II conducted by AICTE. He has been awarded as best faculty in Mechanical Engineering. He has taught subjects such as Engineering Mechanics, Fluid Mechanics, Fluid Machinery, Strength of Material, Human Values, Energy Science, etc.`,
